            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-1082] modify leader election to correctly take into account current epoch</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1082</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when comparing zxids for leader election, the current epoch of the peer needs to be taken into account.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
